{"tid":1244783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[告急]621文宣不足必敗","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T10:54:33.000Z","uid":261627,"like":108,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"029f4b537ba9b4343a08c4362abe0873d8d38c0e","tid":1244783,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:22:59.000Z","msg":"IG得小貓三四張相，真係夠？<br />\n唔求你地做啲咩，簡單文宣都得掛<br />\nIg po個 story 好冇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動搖嘅同我入泥<br />\n<br />\n(求屌醒)621要做乜？我乜都唔知 點解要出？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244018</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mj7WMhd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmj7WMhd.jpg&h=b35fe113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫人推埋<br />\n你好，我唔係任何物資站既admin，不過係前線物資站幫過手<br />\n<br />\n麻煩可唔可以呼籲下除左買裝備送去物資站之外，請大家都帶一套基本裝備(眼罩/口罩/頭盔等)自用，唔好去到物資站先裝身<br />\n裝備壞左先去物資站替換<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以減輕物資站既負擔，有心力時間運送更緊急既物資<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家，一齊努力埋佢"},{"pid":"f8db2bb1659b0178e6a2c1c9320d93fc81e3f222","tid":1244783,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"c997504d447bdabc38408a9cc1fcafbf2631f186","tid":1244783,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"[621]人數與行動的關係<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244761</a>"},{"pid":"84e88abde4bb7a9f1635fe5b91e119204f12ca53","tid":1244783,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8db2bb1659b0178e6a2c1c9320d93fc81e3f222","tid":1244783,"uid":264394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"新 po麻煩推大力 d上熱門"},{"pid":"1910297dea2ce8b6267fe63fcd5cda710d9a240b","tid":1244783,"uid":139593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime